R scripts for making components of Figure S2 of Dreos et al. (PLoS Comput Biol. 2021) 

Input files:

Position probability matrices

   cons_dm6_K6_s1_1.mat
   cons_dm6_K6_s1_2.mat
   cons_dm6_K6_s1_3.mat
   cons_dm6_K6_s1_4.mat
   cons_dm6_K6_s1_5.mat
   cons_dm6_K6_s1_6.mat

Scripts: 

Unmodified scripts from seqLogo R package downloaded from
http://bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/src/contrib/seqLogo_1.54.3.tar.gz

   pwm.R
   seqLogo.R

Modified seqLogo2 function for Figure S3

   seqLogo2_figS2.R

Script to generate the sequence logos for Figure S2 in PDF fromat 

   figS2.R (Usage Rscript --vanilla figS2.R)

Output files:

Sequence logos

   figS2 dm6_class1_logo.pdf
   figS2_dm6_class2_logo.pdf
   figS2_dm6_class3_logo.pdf
   figS2_dm6_class4_logo.pdf
   figS2_dm6_class5_logo.pdf
   figS2_dm6_class6_logo.pdf
